data.description: Blend updates with character in this move-in ready! Offers 2,980 sq ft living space, some new luxury vinyl plank flooring, storage through out, finished basement, fenced exceptionally spacious yard & more. Kitchen furnished with ample cabinetry, large center island, pantry & storage and a lovely breakfast area. Formal dining room flows seamlessly into the space with classic look, ideal for entertaining. Living spaces include a living room with brick fireplace, and a den which can serve a number of different uses. Upstairs enjoy four spacious bedrooms include a master suite with vaulted ceiling. Outdoors you're sure to be pleased by the recreational space available which overlooks the fenced yard, patio & garden - perfect for al fresco BBQs! Finished lower level offers sizable rec room with bath & storage area. Located in friendly neighborhood, this home balances lovely updates & charming classic touches well.
